				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/B%C3%ACnh-l%E1%BB%97-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-qu%C3%A2n-th%C3%AA/poem-vQ6iS8SgAnpHHeUJCdBWUA">Bình lỗ tướng quân thê - 平虜將軍妻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%C3%A1n-Si%C3%AAu/C%E1%BB%95-t%C3%ADch-th%E1%BA%A7n-t%E1%BB%AB-bi-k%C3%BD/poem-VfQsBh5YWl5of84MPx_PIw">Cổ tích thần từ bi ký - 古跡神祠碑記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%C3%A1n-Si%C3%AAu/author-8OezdZDSC-q-9wfu_BOuVw">Trương Hán Siêu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/%C4%90%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C4%90%E1%BB%93-Tri%E1%BB%87u-Vi%C3%AAm-thi%E1%BA%BFu-ph%E1%BB%A7-ph%E1%BA%A5n-%C4%91%E1%BB%93-s%C6%A1n-thu%E1%BB%B7-ca/poem-QP2kBK_qLMSsvg269jP2kA">Đương Đồ Triệu Viêm thiếu phủ phấn đồ sơn thuỷ ca - 當涂趙炎少府粉圖山水歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/H%C3%A0n-th%E1%BB%B1c-t%E1%BB%A9c-h%E1%BB%A9ng/poem-FYmqNXWPYBKhYlTbAKI8aQ">Hàn thực tức hứng - 寒食即興</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/author-geNjG6kbAxWPLaqdF181sQ">Phan Huy Ích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/K%C3%BD-B%C3%A0nh-Ch%C3%A2u-Cao-tam-th%E1%BA%ADp-ng%C5%A9-s%E1%BB%A9-qu%C3%A2n-Th%C3%ADch-H%C3%A0o-Ch%C3%A2u-S%E1%BA%A7m-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-th%E1%BA%A5t-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng-s%E1%BB%AD-Tham-tam-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-oZgRt6bHZRvYsxtU3N2kaQ">Ký Bành Châu Cao tam thập ngũ sứ quân Thích, Hào Châu Sầm nhị thập thất trưởng sử Tham tam thập vận - 寄彭州高三十五使君適、虢州岑二十七長史參三十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%B9i-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-L%E1%BB%8Bch/Li%E1%BB%87t-S%C6%A1n-th%C3%A0nh-c%E1%BA%A3m-c%E1%BB%B1u/poem-Qap3ctw1HVozGXN4m8c1VA">Liệt Sơn thành cảm cựu - 烈山城感舊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%C3%B9i-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-L%E1%BB%8Bch/author-c6g39E3xPTFyf_DWOB-GYw">Bùi Dương Lịch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-Ph%C3%BA/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-ho%E1%BA%A1-ng%E1%BB%B1-ch%E1%BA%BF-Tr%C3%BA-Thu%C3%BD-%C3%81i-ch%C3%A2u/poem-ZVkZllpYGoIDXXstEdAPkg">Phụng hoạ ngự chế “Trú Thuý Ái châu” - 奉和御製駐翠靄洲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-Ph%C3%BA/author-6psImpn4SbleLfrcnYcyQA">Phạm Đạo Phú</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-Mai/Qu%E1%BA%BF-lang-quy-h%E1%BA%ADu-th%E1%BB%8B-t%E1%BB%8Bch-kh%C3%A1ch-ng%E1%BB%A5-v%C5%A9-nhi%C3%AAn-b%E1%BA%A5t-n%C4%83ng-th%C3%A0nh-m%E1%BB%8B-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-6AvUKNW3pqkYfaKO4tWTZQ">Quế lang quy hậu thị tịch khách ngụ vũ nhiên bất năng thành mị kỳ 2 - 桂郎歸後是夕客寓憮然不能成寐其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-Mai/author-0wWyWXBTsjFesQNO4r2tUQ">Viên Mai</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/V%C4%83n-thung-m%E1%BB%85-thanh/poem-qyqmLovWHJ6A84cGasfkVA">Văn thung mễ thanh - 聞舂米聲</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/author-a7YEflJr1_rcFKC9dgECgQ">Hồ Chí Minh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-C%C3%B4n/V%E1%BB%8Dng-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng/poem-wJvMhctGGjp5x0fO5FyMJw">Vọng tưởng - 望想</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BA%B7ng-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-C%C3%B4n/author-5S8czaSOqXhHlNE7NtKr8g">Đặng Trần Côn</a>)<br></div>	</div>
